# group-management

Group Management System (Importance: 80/100)
Path: src/app/groups/[id]/page.tsx

Key Components:

1. Access Control Model
- Public/private group classification system
- Host privilege management with multi-level permissions
- Member status tracking (pending/approved/rejected/left)
- Custom visibility rules for different group types

2. Capacity Management
- Dynamic attendance limits based on group type
- Real-time member count tracking
- Waitlist functionality when capacity reached
- Automatic member pruning for inactive accounts

3. Group Type Classifications
- Specialized group categories (Hangout, Party, Sports)
- Type-specific validation rules and requirements
- Custom member limit rules per category
- Category-based privacy defaults

4. Member Relationship Model
- Host/Member/Pending role system
- Group-specific blocking capabilities
- Cross-reference with user privacy settings
- Member history tracking for rejoins

5. Location Integration
- Group location verification system
- Distance-based discovery rules
- Location privacy controls for group visibility
- Geofencing for physical events

Core Business Rules:
- Groups limited to 150 active members
- Hosts can designate up to 3 co-hosts
- Private groups require member approval
- Location sharing mandatory for physical events
- Member pruning after 30 days inactivity
- Host status transferable to active members

